$r = Formula("-$kn/$kn2")->reduce;
#$r   = Formula("(1-$b-$n)*$n/($a*$n2*$n1)")->reduce;
$y0 = Compute(non_zero_random(-9,9));
$y1 = Compute(non_zero_random(-9,9));

BEGIN_TEXT
$BBOLD (2) $EBOLD
Substituting \(y = \sum_{n=0}^{\infty}c_n\ x^n\) into 
\((x^2 + $a) y'' + $b x y' =0\), you get that
\{ BeginTable(center=>0).
